      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for the right owner. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable surface scratches and a few small dings, while the interior has some visible wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it lacks the polish of a newer or better-maintained model. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
